header.title: The Catcher in the Rye
header.creator: Amelia Lamargese, Alessandra Trenchi, Rayes Seif, and Juan Pablo Casado
header.description: An ontology representing concepts and relationships from the novel 'The Catcher in the Rye'.

comments.en: An ontology for representing expressions of place in the context of 'Catcher in the Rye'

additionalInformation.value: This ontology was created as part of a collaborative project for the course Knowledge Representation and Extraction for the DHK programm in University of Bologna.
